{"tid":661961,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"Fight League 交鋒聯盟","createTime":"2018-05-12T04:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T23:50:47.000Z","uid":31105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e7393182675610d5c88d4ee8981f13448a3ed07e","tid":661961,"uid":31105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:26:52.000Z","msg":"因為舊果個TG gp 無左, 而家重開同埋想多D人玩<br />\n<strong>Link : <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AuLn8lNguOn5pt9GkTRjWw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAuLn8lNguOn5pt9GkTRjWw&d=3juTG67kHkovhAVMyh4CYr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d6786500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AuLn8lNguOn5pt9GkTRjWw</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/122503_1ac994ef562df5d0f66d2786011ed427.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F122503_1ac994ef562df5d0f66d2786011ed427.png&h=cecb77a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎緊既update : <br />\n<br />\n關於「快速上手交鋒聯盟」一部分關卡調整<br />\n<br />\n※本文皆為日本時間<br />\n我們對CPU戰「快速上手交鋒聯盟」的 關卡進行了一些調整。<br />\n關卡調整後，交鋒好手們可更加容易體驗到 交鋒聯盟的玩法、各種族的戰鬥方法等內容。<br />\n而隨著難易度的調整， 通關可獲得的「交鋒卡」及「US級鬥士」獎勵 也將更容易取得！<br />\n<br />\n未來營運團隊也會為了增進遊戲體驗， 持續調整「快速上手交鋒聯盟」。<br />\n<br />\n◎關於「快速上手交鋒聯盟」請點這裡<br />\n<br />\n▼調整對象<br />\nCPU戰「快速上手交鋒聯盟」一部分關卡<br />\n<br />\n▼調整內容<br />\n・各關卡的難易度調整 <br />\n・變更一部分攻略提示和主要內容<br />\n<br />\n※「快速上手交鋒聯盟」調整後， 即使突破已通關的關卡也無法再次獲得獎勵。<br />\n<br />\n▼預計完成調整時間<br />\n2018/5/14 19:00 左右<br />\n<br />\n官方網站 : <a href=\"https://fight-league.com/tc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffight-league.com%2Ftc%2F&d=3juTG67kHkovhAVMyh4CYr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=4dd5b5d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fight-league.com/tc/</a><br />\n官方Facebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FightLeagueOfficialTC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFightLeagueOfficialTC%2F&d=3juTG67kHkovhAVMyh4CYr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f8c78883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FightLeagueOfficialTC/</a>"},{"pid":"68a7ba864e21038a5637c237b316d6c5672b4d38","tid":661961,"uid":31105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T00:53:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"17f34118d83bd3458412ef765b95064224f4e98a","tid":661961,"uid":31105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:58:34.000Z","msg":"Push 新pool 已出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be433a5edc6c6c5534d182b346becf3dd7a7b88","tid":661961,"uid":9613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"b1aaaf3e14a7fcf791ac97261832c9c67f5e62dd","tid":661961,"uid":124876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"32005948839a7acad6d15f2c5fa09edd38bff9b4","tid":661961,"uid":9613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/135449_7daddd076609c33f165474d38381923a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F135449_7daddd076609c33f165474d38381923a.png&h=32a6c7f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb90080b7ccee7af0ee41706c2837c27dc95b179","tid":661961,"uid":31105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1aaaf3e14a7fcf791ac97261832c9c67f5e62dd","tid":661961,"uid":124876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:04:04.000Z","msg":"有玩可以入gp 交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7313ce030bc7c37b632fe70d14a04779e2fab167","tid":661961,"uid":9613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb90080b7ccee7af0ee41706c2837c27dc95b179","tid":661961,"uid":31105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":